edge: Housefull 2 is a Bollywood film released in 2012, and its soundtrack is also known as Housefull 2 Soundtrack.
Sandeep Shirodkar composed the film score for Housefull 2.
Label T-Series released the soundtrack album of Housefull 2.
Sajid–Wajid composed all music for the Housefull 2 soundtrack album.
Neeraj Shridhar sang "Papa Toh Band Bajaye", a song from the Housefull 2 soundtrack album.
Mamta Sharma sang "Anarkali Disco Chali", a song from the Housefull 2 soundtrack album.
Sukhwinder Singh sang "Anarkali Disco Chali", a song from the Housefull 2 soundtrack album.
Wajid Khan, along with Sunidhi Chauhan and Suzanne D'Mello, sang "Right Now Now", a song from the Housefull 2 soundtrack album.
Shaan sang "Do U Know", a song from the Housefull 2 soundtrack album.
Shreya Ghoshal sang "Do U Know", a song from the Housefull 2 soundtrack album.
A remixed version of "Anarkali Disco Chali" was included in the Housefull 2 soundtrack album, known as "Anarkali Disco Chali" (Hyper Mix).
A remixed version of "Right Now Now" was included in the Housefull 2 soundtrack album, known as "Right Now Now" (Remix).
A remixed version of "Anarkali Disco Chali" was included in the Housefull 2 soundtrack album, known as "Anarkali Disco Chali" (Remix).
